519
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:55,960
help me grow even more. And you can get some 
amazing things out of people when you just treat  

520
00:39:55,960 --> 00:40:04,320
them with the respect. I assume that everyone 
I talk to, everyone I talk to is interesting,  

521
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:07,960
has seeds of greatness in them, even if they 
don't recognize necessarily where they are. 

522
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:13,080
Someone described to me actually this morning 
in one of my little dirt clubs I run about they  

